OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fdry through the evening with largely
OL,7,Fclear skies. Staying dry with mostly
OL,8,Fclear skies overnight. Becoming windy
OL,9,Fin the southwest and around the coasts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FDry with some spells of
OL,12,Fsunshine, although some high cloud
OL,13,Faround. A warm day but cooler along
OL,14,Fsoutheastern facing coasts.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,17,Fon Wednesday although rather cloudy in
OL,18,Fthe east. Colder on Thursday with rain
OL,19,Ffollowed by showers. Rain likely on
OL,20,FFriday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
